{"tid":61363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊度過今日，特別係頭上有帽果啲同我入哂黎","createTime":"2016-12-31T07:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T11:38:25.000Z","uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc0e65379fc7526fa0c4dee86c9e6e905b8a1cb","tid":61363,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"今日可能係最後一次見佢了，好難過，坐左係公園兩粒鐘，等緊佢地出現，還錢俾我，就可以沒有然後了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過戴左帽之後發現，自己一定要發奮圖強，做個有實力既男人，將來唔係要去搶其他人既女人，而係好好守護自己既女人<br />\n<br />\n受過情傷既大家，希望大家都放低仇恨，努力增強自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾經想俾壓力去拆散你地，好對唔住，原來你快樂，我先會快樂 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝各位明年開始事事順利，巴打既就升職加薪，有女埋身，對你日日都咁真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n絲打既，事業成凰，愛情浴春風，一世唔會lone <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝所有人，幸福、快樂"},{"pid":"72cc8c33630693f06779e70b1f8579e1d0df5a4c","tid":61363,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:59:27.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"b934e8a839708e90ed3fb87aaa8b93d7aeffab10","tid":61363,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:15:17.000Z","msg":"冇人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5f138913a79d3b877a8d39c7c1ef917c4d0c50","tid":61363,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"巴打,happy 撩 ear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b546a1c3032571284ee17ee7e18988cb4e8ee37","tid":61363,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"個女人還清錢未？"},{"pid":"bf340d063131dd0f77a6548437